snippet.title: FISHBANE Game Playthrough 1-3
snippet.description:
Request a game by leaving a comment or a pm. I will play pretty much anything.

This is FISHBANE by Droqen. It is about this scuba diver collecting the golden harpoons while getting fish along the way.

You can play it here: http://www.newgrounds.com/portal/view/541803 more parts to come.
